Company Overview of Waterfall Asset Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Waterfall Asset Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm provides its services to investment companies, pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, corporations, state or municipal government entities, and insurance companies. It manages separate-client focused portfolios. The firm invests fixed income markets across the globe. It invests in asset-backed securities and mortgage-backed securities. The firm employs distressed/vulture, loan, and absolute return strategy to make its investments. It employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolios. The firm employs a combination of in-house and external research to ma...
Waterfall Asset Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm provides its services to investment companies, pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, corporations, state or municipal government entities, and insurance companies. It manages separate-client focused portfolios. The firm invests fixed income markets across the globe. It invests in asset-backed securities and mortgage-backed securities. The firm employs distressed/vulture, loan, and absolute return strategy to make its investments. It employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolios. The firm employs a combination of in-house and external research to make its investments. Waterfall Asset Management, LLC was founded on November 30, 2004 and is based in New York City.
