Waterfall Asset Management Announces Establishment of London Office; Announces Executive Appointments
Mar 10 16
Waterfall Asset Management announced to establish a London office of Waterfall.

Messers Cuby and Malmer will act as co-heads of the office. Cuby and Malmer provide a wealth of experience within the structured credit sector and the banking industry, having spent the last ten years at Investec Bank PLC, where they established and ran Investec's Credit Investments business. Cuby and Malmer will seek to expand Waterfall's structured credit and direct lending business in the European market.


